  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC271">
          <l>acainilaik kiḷavi yākuvaḻi yaṟital.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/166/mode/1up">166</ref>.</p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <p>
itu,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC271-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘cella maṉṉār neṭuntakai’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum.   (23)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n217/mode/1up">214</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i – ḷ. āraikkiḷavi acainilaiyāmiṭamaṟika. e–ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
u – m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC271-Cena-cit1">
        <l>‘peyari ṉākiya tokaiyumā ruḷavē<app><note>(col. 67)</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e–m.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC271-Cena-cit2">
        <l>ellā vuyiroṭuñ cellumār mutalē<app><note>(eḻut. 61)</note></app></l>
      </lg>
      <p>
e–m. varum.
      </p>
      <p>
ākuvaḻiyaṟitaleṉṟataṉāl, acainilaiyāṅkāl ummai muṉṉarum ummīṟṟuviṉaimuṉṉarumallatu vārāmaiyaṟika. ciṟupāṉmai piṟāṇṭu varumēṉuṅkoḷka.	(23)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/298/mode/1up">298</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, mēlataṟkōr puṟaṉaṭai
      </p>
      <p>
(i–ḷ) acainilaik kiḷavi yākuvaḻiyaṟital ― avvāreṉṉuñ col lacainilaiccollā miṭamaṟikaveṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
‘ākuvaḻi’ yaṟitaleṉṟataṉāṉummai muṉṉarum ‘um’ īṟṟu viṉai muṉṉarum varutalkoḷka.
      </p>
      <p>
(u–m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC271-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>‘peyari ṉākiya tokaiyumā ruḷavē’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC271-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>‘ellā vuyiroṭuñ cellumār mutalē’</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum.
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
